beets is installed via pipx.
beets requires Python 3.12.

Getting started:

```
pipx install --python python3.12 beets
```

Full initial install:

```
pipx install --python python3.12 beets[autobpm,chroma,discogs,embedart,fetchart,import,lastgenre,lyrics,mpdstats,scrub,web]
```

Adding dependencies:

```
pipx inject --include-apps beets beetcamp python-mpd2
pipx inject beets beets-audible beets-copyartifacts3
```
